284
00:17:21,140 --> 00:17:22,610
I'm back.

285
00:17:22,610 --> 00:17:23,450
Welcome back.

286
00:17:23,450 --> 00:17:24,190
Welcome back.

287
00:17:24,190 --> 00:17:26,900
