Apparently the clerk remembered the number.

295
00:17:48,080 --> 00:17:50,480
Huh? After seeing it only once and briefly?

296
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:54,660
It happened to be their birthday, 1022.

297
00:17:55,230 --> 00:17:56,390
What?

298
00:17:56,390 --> 00:17:58,210
Wow.

299
00:18:08,650 --> 00:18:13,030
A high school girl has gone missing
in Nerima City, Tokyo.

300
00:18:13,690 --> 00:18:16,620
She has been unreachable
since she left her home late at night

301
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:18,080
two days ago on the 4th of this month.

302
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:20,730
The next morning, her family…

303
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:25,750
We, the Homosapiens, just received
the results of Round 1 of the N-1.

304
00:18:25,750 --> 00:18:27,260
And would you believe it? We passed!

305
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:28,350
Of course we did.

306
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:30,050
Even amateurs could make it past Round 1.

307
00:18:30,050 --> 00:18:31,890
Where do you think the finish line is?

308
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:37,800
Equator Sauna

309
00:18:31,890 --> 00:18:34,100
But last year, we failed in Round 2.

310
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:35,400
After ten years in the business...

311
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:44,560
Equator Sauna

312
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:52,570
Who is it?

313
00:18:52,570 --> 00:18:54,870
We work for Ibusuki.

314
00:19:02,890 --> 00:19:04,120
Hello.

315
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:07,280
Hello.

316
00:19:08,950 --> 00:19:12,870
You look young. Have a seat.

317
00:19:12,870 --> 00:19:14,100
Excuse us.

318
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:18,660
So?

319
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:25,950
We need a remote monitoring
dash cam and GPS installed.

320
00:19:25,950 --> 00:19:29,810
What? Hold on. That's totally illegal.

321
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:31,510
Where?

322
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:36,740
His car. This is the dash cam.

323
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:41,640
It's a common model.

324
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,660
You'll install it, won't you?

325
00:19:43,660 --> 00:19:46,020
If you pay for it.

326
00:19:46,410 --> 00:19:47,730
You'll be paid tomorrow.

327
00:19:47,730 --> 00:19:52,450
No can do. Equator operates 24 hours
a day, but that's just the sauna.

328
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:54,800
How long will it take?

329
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:58,120
I'm busy. Give me three days.

330
00:19:58,120 --> 00:19:59,840
Make it one.

331
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:04,330
1.5 days, or pay a rush late night surcharge.

332
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:05,940
How much?

333
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:10,410
550,000. And I'll need your help, too.

334
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:18,620
Pretty old car.
Didn't need all these tools.

335
00:20:26,910 --> 00:20:29,040
How long will it take?

336
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:33,700
About seven or eight minutes.

337
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:35,080
Seven or eight minutes?

338
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:36,010
Yeah.

339
00:20:46,010 --> 00:20:47,080
What is it?

340
00:20:48,630 --> 00:20:50,140
Are you hungry?

341
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,740
Hold on.

342
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:00,490
Okay, all good.

343
00:21:04,840 --> 00:21:07,810
That should do it.

344
00:21:08,130 --> 00:21:12,970
Fine. I'll go buy you something.
Stay put and be good.

345
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,320
Crap, crap, crap.

346
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:26,020
Odokawa's coming, Odokawa's
coming, Odokawa's coming!

347
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:27,700
Crap, crap, crap!

348
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:29,160
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

349
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:35,200
Was he really talking to someone?

350
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:40,240
Yeah. He even ominously told them
to “stay put and be good.”

351
00:21:42,970 --> 00:21:48,980
Anyway, I could imagine him kidnapping
and holding someone as cute as her

352
00:21:48,980 --> 00:21:51,710
if she happened to get in his taxi.

353
00:21:51,710 --> 00:21:55,940
He may be involved, but kidnapping
 and false imprisonment?

354
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:58,430
No, you're right. I guess not.

355
00:22:00,730 --> 00:22:03,170
Did you call her cute?

