00:22:06,670 --> 00:22:09,970
Yeah, didn't you just say that?

358
00:22:11,820 --> 00:22:13,410
No, you definitely did.

359
00:22:13,410 --> 00:22:13,860
What?

360
00:22:13,860 --> 00:22:16,410
Her photo hasn't appeared on the news yet.

361
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:17,930
Why'd you say that?

362
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:18,780
I didn't say that.

363
00:22:18,780 --> 00:22:19,910
No, you did.

364
00:22:21,250 --> 00:22:23,430
What? Really?

365
00:22:23,430 --> 00:22:24,180
Yeah.

366
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,270
